<a href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/health/canadian-surgeons-face-flat-lining-job-market/article1920006/" title="Feb 24, 2011 8:57PM EST - Rejected by small and large cities alike, recent graduates with huge debt loads are creating the latest specialty in medicine: the on-call-ogist" class="sans sm" name="&lpos=Widget - Additional Content - Most Popular&lid=5" onClick="s_objectID='';">Canadian surgeons face flat-lining job market</a>
</li>
</ol>
